metadata.name: HMV#012
metadata.description: The Homoversians (HMV) offers it's 777 HMV NFT holders (aka HMV Primes) the chance to access Agent0's Metapulse airdrop, access to Starlight (heartbeat regulated Wallet without a seed phrase), and a prime access card to create their own metapulse (heartbeat token).By burning Agent0's metapulses, the 777 dynamic HMV NFTs will evolve  through 8 stages of evolution giving holders higher levels of access to a world of infinite possibilities
